      "title": "Commentary: Micron’s massive profits are a guarantee of trouble",
      "summary": "SK hynix 관련 기사다. 기사 제목은 'Commentary: Micron’s massive profits are a guarantee of trouble'이다. Chip scarcity is forcing up memory prices and making the likes of Micron and SK Hynix astonishingly profitable. That's a guarantee of trouble, says Chris Bryant for Bloomberg Opinion. This scarcity is forcing up memory prices and making Micron, SK Hynix and Samsung Electronics astonishingly profitable But customers are unhappy, governments could intervene and shortages may open the door to Chinese rivals After a surge in memory costs, action-camera maker GoPro has warned about its ability to continue as a going concern BOILING TENSIONS SK Hynix, which raised tens of billions of dollars in a US share sale this week , warned in its prospectus about the danger of “government inquiries, civil litigations, increased regulatory oversight, new or modified conditions on government incentives or subsidies, or legislative or executive actions that could affect how we manufacture, price, allocate or distribute our products” Similarly, Micron’s recent US filings highlight the peril of long-term customer relationships becoming strained and “downstream” markets that rely on its products being disrupted, as well as possible legal disputes and greater “government and regulatory focus”. 이 기사는 해당 기업과 연결된 해외 보도를 바탕으로 정리했다.",
